data.description: You do not want to miss your opportunity on this immaculately kept cottage beauty near LSU! This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is perfectly situated and includes hardwood floors, crown molding throughout and so much more.  You are met with an old world charm as soon as you enter.  There is so much room in this home for your get-togethers with family and friends.  There is plenty of seating available with its multiple entertaining areas and grand stairs.  All of the bedrooms are spacious and the bathrooms have ceramic tile.  The kitchen is the heart of the home and has exposed brick and also a second sitting area for gathering while you cook for your guests.  Upstairs provides two more bedrooms and a bathroom as well as wood flooring and lots of space for guests.  Outside you will find a separate partial mother-in-law suite.  Just add a kitchen and shower and this could be great income potential or give your guest their own private space to enjoy.  You don't want to miss this home; schedule your showing today, it won't last long!
